name: Tirta
description:
Formed in water, 

Tirta became one of the highly skilled healer under the Saka Kingdom led by Prabu Saar. With his calm and wisdom, Queen Tyas likes Tirta. But Prabu didn't seem to care about Tirta. 

Until one day, during the war, Prabu Saar was dying of an illness which could be cured with a Holy Relic (Keris). Queen Tyas decided to send Bara and Tirta on an expedition to find Keris.
